                        <div align="center">
                          <p align="left">Birth date:  April 19th 1999. Created Character on Bertoxx to play with some RL friends, was on Bristlebain for about 3 weeks prior with my Barb Warrior Landane (still level 6).  I have been in 3 different guilds, Holy Crusaders, which split to form Flaming Blade of Truth, which merged with Healers of Norrath.  So while the guild name has changed and I have picked up new friends with each change a large percentage of each guild has been the same folks.  The first person I grouped with regularly was Jagir (Clearskys), other old school groupmates are Yilmatin, Camaxtli, Cillius, Patience, Tueton (RIP), and Vampiro.  I can usually be found in the company of my RL wife's Ranger, Mekare.  She uses me for invis undead and to keep the gnomes off her.  :-)</p>
